---
title: Steak Sandwiches with Horseradish Mayo plus Crispy Fried Onions & Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Get ready to whip up this restaurant-worthy steak sandwich with just six ingredients and a quick 25 minutes on the clock. You’ll layer juicy sliced steak with crispy fried onions on chewy toasted ciabatta rolls slathered with zesty horseradish mayo (a classic combo!). But it wouldn’t be a slam dunk without a side dish, and that’s why this sumptuous sammie is served with tender roasted sweet potato wedges (and more of that zingy horseradish sauce for dipping).
